    "Title": "Missing: ~mission(TargetName)",
    "Description": "Unfortunately, one of our community partners, ~mission(TargetName), has been missing for a few days. Their family contacted Citizens for Prosperity for help and I told them we would do what we could. That said, with so much time passed, I\u2019m not too hopeful.\n\nWhatever their current state is, we're looking for someone to be our eyes on the ground for this one. There\u2019s a strong chance that they were headed to ~mission(Location|Address), an area known to be very dangerous.\n\nIf you can track them down and confirm their status, one way or another, I\u2019ll see that you\u2019re properly compensated.\n\nLima Endicott\nLead Dispatcher\nCitizens for Prosperity",
